		   	<h3>Design</h3>		
				<p>I provide design that is both engaging and usable. From research on your current/prospective users, I produce website/app designs of the information architecture, with content and functionality as wireframes/prototypes to observe usability and improvements with user testing. These are refined until I know the product meets both your system and your current/prospective users requirements. I'm adaptable to using a wide range of illustrator and image editor packages. Have used the Adobe Illustrator suite and currently I use Axure RP Pro 7, GIMP 2.6 and Inkscape on a day to day basis.</p>
